## 5. Getting Started

1. Run `describe_workspace(config="{{ smak_config_path }}")` to see available indices
2. Use `search(config="{{ smak_config_path }}", query="...", index="...")` to explore
3. When you understand a symbol's purpose, enrich it (see the `enrichment-protocol` skill)
4. Run `/power-level` periodically to track progress
5. Run `/regenerate` after significant enrichment to update this skill
